              <ipxact:description>ACS Violation Status.
ACS Violations may occur due to either hardware or software defects/failures. The ACS Violation Status bit prvides positive identification of the errr.
 The contrller sets this bit when your application asserts app_err_bus[12].
Note: This register field is sticky.</ipxact:description>
