            </ipxact:field>
            <ipxact:field>
              <ipxact:name>first_dword_third_byte</ipxact:name>
              <ipxact:description>Byte 2 of Header log register of First 32-bit Data wrd.
This field represents third byte of First DW of Header.
Note: This register field is sticky.</ipxact:description>
