              <ipxact:description>Equalization 16.0GT/s Phase 1 Successful.
For a Multi-Function Upstream Port, this bit must be implemented in Function 0 and RsvdZ in other Functions.
Note: This register field is sticky.</ipxact:description>
              <ipxact:bitOffset>1</ipxact:bitOffset>
              <ipxact:resets>
                <ipxact:reset>
                  <ipxact:value>0x0</ipxact:value>
