              <ipxact:description>PTM Requester Propagation Delay Byte Reversal. Reverse the order of bytes in the PTM Propagation Delay data word of the PTM ResponseD Message, for compatibility with previous revisions.
For more information, see the PTM section in the Databook.
Note: This register field is sticky.</ipxact:description>
