              <ipxact:name>ptm_req_clock_corr_msb</ipxact:name>
              <ipxact:description>PTM Requester Clock Correction MSB.
Upper 32 bits of amount by which PTM Requester Local Clock has been corrected.
For more information, see the PTM section in the Databook.
Note: This register field is sticky.</ipxact:description>
              <ipxact:bitOffset>0</ipxact:bitOffset>
              <ipxact:resets>
