            <ipxact:field>
              <ipxact:name>ptm_req_nom_clock_t_int</ipxact:name>
              <ipxact:description>PTM Requester Nominal Clock Period Integral.
Integral part of the nominal PTM local clock period. LSB is 1/(2^16) nanoseconds.
For more information, see the PTM section in the Databook.
Note: This register field is sticky.</ipxact:description>
              <ipxact:bitOffset>16</ipxact:bitOffset>
              <ipxact:resets>
